4.2. Aspect
An aspect is a modularization of a concern that cuts across multiple classes. 
logging can be an example of such cross-cutting concern.
transaction

Joinpoint: where you can apply


Pointcut : where you have applied




Advice:
before
after
around


Weaving: 



LoanService       ---------------->  LoanServiceProxy extends LogService
     issueLoan()                     before
                                      super.issueLoan();
                                    
                                    after



